{"tid":2330992,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"撐澳洲政府同中國打貿易戰 澳超市Kmart下架所有中國商品","createTime":"2020-12-18T12:11:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-18T13:26:05.000Z","uid":36494,"like":26,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5cccb9ecb762f45e9d77cdbf4b01079cea782c54","tid":2330992,"uid":36494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:11:53.000Z","msg":"中澳貿易衝突持續升級，澳洲零售巨頭Wesfarmers（ASX: WES）旗下的連鎖零售商店Kmart為力挺澳洲，宣佈將清空店内所有中國製的商品，有澳洲傳媒預期Kmart的這一舉措可能會引發其他零售商如Target（NYSE: TGT）、Bunning與Big W的跟隨。<br />\n<br />\n澳媒《The Shovel》引述Kmart公司發言人報道，撤下中國製商品的決定是一項非常重要的表態，並稱這只是該公司對澳洲政府表達支持的一件小事。該發言人亦補充，接下來Kmart 將陸續下架中國製的服裝、家居產品、電器、玩具以及體育用品等，隨後再撤下其他中國製造的聖誕節裝飾、寵物用品與文具等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n該發言人透露，在下架上述商品後，他們只需移除所有中國製的貨架、燈飾、地板、購物推車和更衣室的布簾就大功告成，並表示民衆幾乎不會看出有任何變化。另外，Kmart亦表示，儘管已撤下所有中國製產品，店内依舊還有大量商品供顧客購買，並稱如今所有的自助結賬櫃檯都是日本製造。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://businessfocus.io/article/153942/kmart-%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E5%95%86%E5%93%81\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbusinessfocus.io%2Farticle%2F153942%2Fkmart-%25E6%25B8%2585%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%25A3%25BD%25E5%2595%2586%25E5%2593%2581&d=PGKZrCzpIeFm7bz4D1EKracrr%2FRj6%2FCkFD6x6yFTuc4%3D&h=d68103ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://businessfocus.io/article/153942/kmart-%E6%B8%85%E7%A9%BA%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E8%A3%BD%E5%95%86%E5%93%81</a>"},{"pid":"2ac2898c9be0241744b016fc11e6d5146118823f","tid":2330992,"uid":36494,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:12:17.000Z","msg":"雖然有外界認為Kmart的這個舉措是「把鷄蛋放在一個籃子裏」，但Kmart打趣回應，事實上他們的籃子是中國製的，因此並沒有將任何東西放在籃子裏。報導亦預計Wesfarmers旗下的其他零售商店如Target與Bunnings和Woolworths（ASX: WOW）旗下的Big W將陸續跟隨Kmart的脚步，宣佈類似相關決策。<br />\n<br />\n根據英國《每日郵報》指出，Kmart作為澳洲知名的零售品牌之一，以衆多平價產品吸引了大批消費者，然而其低價的原因是因為部分產品都是在中國製造。隨著新冠肺炎疫情爆發，KMart於6月時掀起了一股搶購潮，不少商品也被搶購一空，導致各個貨架連續幾周空空如也，引起衆多消費者不滿。<br />\n<br />\nText by BusinessFocus Editorial"},{"pid":"766e349f6380da6080838197cede60196a8dabc3","tid":2330992,"uid":122275,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5cc8d21846b1787610f190ecef1a8ab2e25efa21","tid":2330992,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:13:41.000Z","msg":"Fake news 嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n過隔嚟post有人講<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2330969\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2330969</a>"},{"pid":"bd84bbfc30c44c88c911f6853bb661b9f5f46825","tid":2330992,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:14:38.000Z","msg":"幾時停埋中國留學生 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static01-proxy.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2625000/2629153/042_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic01-proxy.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2625000%2F2629153%2F042_1024.jpg&h=dfc73af5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/cis/5d579f522e39591811a8a1ec.jpg/Ng0WA28VBMYE1MLcwZfQ69y4qyEnLqORyPoBs8j6AbM?v=w1920r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fcis%2F5d579f522e39591811a8a1ec.jpg%2FNg0WA28VBMYE1MLcwZfQ69y4qyEnLqORyPoBs8j6AbM%3Fv%3Dw1920r16_9&h=15f083f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d0869f00812adb864ba26f9a152ffdbca6ffa42","tid":2330992,"uid":189046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f025e59cee79cae7edab13e0ae0bb031e035093","tid":2330992,"uid":307270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-18T12:15:23.000Z","msg":"Fake news, 請查source"},{"pid":"c41bea261fee17c52